com.google.wave.api.event
Interface EventHandler

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractRobot
public interface EventHandler

An interface for robot event handler. This interface defines various methods that would respond to all possible robot events.

Nested Class Summary
static interface EventHandler.Capability
          An annotation that would define the robot's interest in handling a particular event.
